@startuml Video_Call_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> RequestingPermissions : Check Camera/Microphone Permissions
RequestingPermissions --> PermissionDenied : Permission Denied
RequestingPermissions --> PermissionGranted : Permission Granted

PermissionDenied --> RequestingPermissions : Request Permission Again
PermissionGranted --> InitializingCall : Setup Camera/Microphone

InitializingCall --> Connecting : Start Video Call
Connecting --> Connected : Connection Established
Connecting --> ConnectionFailed : Connection Failed

Connected --> VideoCalling : Video Call Active
VideoCalling --> Muting : Mute Button Clicked
VideoCalling --> Unmuting : Unmute Button Clicked
VideoCalling --> SwitchingCamera : Switch Camera Button Clicked
VideoCalling --> EndingCall : End Call Button Clicked

Muting --> VideoCalling : Microphone Muted
Unmuting --> VideoCalling : Microphone Unmuted
SwitchingCamera --> VideoCalling : Camera Switched

EndingCall --> CallEnded : Call Terminated
ConnectionFailed --> CallEnded : Show Error Message

CallEnded --> [*] : Activity Finished

@enduml
